      "description": "The Teucrium Agricultural Fund (TAGS) is an exchange-traded fund that is based on the Teucrium TAGS index. The fund is a fund-of-funds that invests directly in the four Teucrium commodity funds. The fund rebalances daily to provide equal exposure to corn, wheat, sugar and soybeans. TAGS was launched on Mar 28, 2012 and is issued by Teucrium.",
